i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxwbMjqg.jpg&h=69892f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（15日）是「全民國家安全教育日」，香港警察學院舉行開放日活動。19歲的黎同學和朋友特地前來，觀看警隊各項表演和裝備展示。黎同學表示，印象最深刻的項目是飛虎隊反恐演習，「平時很難有機會看到飛虎隊員遊繩執行任務，近距離看到他們對付恐怖分子的專業行動，令我更加堅定投考警隊的理想。希望將來能夠進入警察機動部隊及四大『皇牌部門』，為維護國家安全貢獻自己的一份力量。」<br />\n<br />\n黎同學還向記者坦言，過去的黑暴活動令他感到痛心，警隊一直在前線盡忠職守，守護家園，保護香港市民，不能理解為什麼有些人要仇警，甚至是殺警，「任何地方有人犯法，警察就要執法」。他強調，香港是國家的一部分，每個人都有責任守衛自己的家園。<br />\n<br />\n黎生個仔?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"四大「皇牌部門」係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"嫖、賭、飲、吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"偷、呃、拐、騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6f4bea98fabe3394f884afca709838772e7128","tid":2491253,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cc668b640a4845522c0c73178731428acd4a66","tid":2491253,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf5d00bdf7d2fc7cd075629475edbd60f48f6fb5","tid":2491253,"uid":1049,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"睇黎過多幾年差佬又會請返夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下一代都甘願投共，仲有咩好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:39:23.000Z","msg":"一個＝下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3526e79d55d151b8a4f14040f269291daf380a17","tid":2491253,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:39:26.000Z","msg":"有位快啲上<img src=\"/ass